TITLE: Basic Cache Usage
DESCRIPTION: Basic example of using FusionCache to get or set a cached product with a 30-second duration
SOURCE: https://github.com/ziggycreatures/fusioncache/blob/main/README.md#2025-04-22_snippet_4

LANGUAGE: csharp
CODE:
```
var id = 42;

cache.GetOrSet<Product>(
	$"product:{id}",
	_ => GetProductFromDb(id),
	TimeSpan.FromSeconds(30)
);
```

