TITLE: Using Fail-Safe with Result Pattern in FusionCache
DESCRIPTION: This example shows how to use the fail-safe mechanism with a Result Pattern approach, avoiding exceptions by using the Fail method on the factory execution context. It sets a custom duration and enables fail-safe.
SOURCE: https://github.com/ziggycreatures/fusioncache/blob/main/docs/FailSafe.md#2025-04-22_snippet_1

LANGUAGE: csharp
CODE:
```
var productResult = await cache.GetOrSetAsync<Result<Product>>(
	$"product:{id}",
	async (ctx, ct) =>
	{
		var productResult = GetProductFromDb(id);

		if (productResult.IsSuccess == false)
		{
			return ctx.Fail(productResult.Error);
		}

		return productResult;
	},
	opt => opt.SetDuration(duration).SetFailSafe(true)
);
```

