TITLE: Registering FusionCache as a Keyed Service in C#
DESCRIPTION: This snippet shows how to register a named FusionCache instance as a keyed service, making it available through both the IFusionCacheProvider and the keyed services mechanism in .NET 8.
SOURCE: https://github.com/ziggycreatures/fusioncache/blob/main/docs/DependencyInjection.md#2025-04-22_snippet_8

LANGUAGE: csharp
