TITLE: Configuring Distributed Cache with Background Operations in FusionCache
DESCRIPTION: Example showing how to configure Redis as a distributed cache with FusionCache and enable background operations. This demonstrates a potential race condition when directly accessing the distributed cache after setting a value with background operations enabled.
